title: Datt inn á þetta fyrir tilviljun

posts.text:
Datt inn á þessa síðu áðan, upplýsingarnar örugglega ekki alveg réttar en samt gaman að þessu.  
 
Countable Data Brief
Vaktin.is is tracked by us since April, 2011. Over the time it has been ranked as high as 351 899 in the world, while most of its traffic comes from Iceland, where it reached as high as 94 position. Spjall.vaktin.is receives about 53.67% of its total traffic. All this time it was owned by Skynet ehf, it was hosted by Hringdu VPS network. 
Spjall.vaktin has a mediocre Google pagerank and bad results in terms of Yandex topical citation index. We found that Spjall.vaktin.is is poorly ‘socialized’ in respect to any social network. According to MyWot, Siteadvisor and Google safe browsing analytics, Spjall.vaktin.is is a fully trustworthy domain with no visitor reviews.
